metadata.name: Prof. NOTA's PFP
metadata.description:
Hi, #OiOi Fams! I'm Prof. NOTA!  
Shush, I'm playing, learning, and working for this PFP.

This PFP was created to remind us to stay alert with our personal security in the Web3 ecosystem. If you like, you can use this PFP as your profile picture, anywhere in the Web3 ecosystem. If you want, you can customize this PFP as you need, but don't monetize it. If you can, please always keep our community safe and beware of scams!

Prof. NOTA doesn't belong in your reality, your real life. In your reality, in your real life, you just can meet the avatar of Prof. NOTA in any version. So, once again, beware of scams!

Regards,

Prof. NOTA
